features: Three different types of nuts will be included for compatibility. Not every soda stream model uses the same thread dimensions for their CO2 connector nut.

Material: Each item is 3D printed with high quality, biodegradable PLA plastic, made from plant materials. All models are paintable! For color consistancy please order all items at the same time. Colors may differ from what they look like online.
Shipping: Once your order is placed, depending on the quantity ordered, it takes 1-5 days for printing and post-processing.

body.description: A 120mm fan bracket for 3x 5.25 inch bays. It mounts with M3 screws just like an optical drive or other 5.25 inch bay accessories. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fit perfectly into 3-5.25” slots and looks great
reviews.reviewText: Needed to add another fan to my old case for a new computer rebuild. Had these three 5.25” slots that were available but no way to add fan without it looking sloppy. Found this bracket which fit perfectly along with recommended cover and fan. All assembled together nicely and was able to increase case intake flow without buying new case for the rebuild. New cases have reduced number of HDD slots.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Fits in the slot snuggly and the holes are accurate enough that my tooless 5.25 bay removal thing had no problems snapping down and holding it into place. The fan attached just fine as well. It doesn't come with a grill to reduce dust entrance to the case, so I ended up ordering a cheap plastic one and super gluing it into place over it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent 5.25" Fan Adapter
reviews.reviewText: This was exactly what I needed for a project case I've been working on for months now. The case lacked upper airflow, so certain parts were getting way too hot. This bracket worked way better than anticipated and looks clean. Absolutely worth the money and deserves the 5 star review.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great 5.25” bay fan expansion
